sources.title: Dawn on the Great Divide 1942 (Western movie) Buck Jones & Raymond Hatton | Rough Riders series
sources.description:
Epic adventure of the scouts who blazed covered wagon trails... and the reckless women who fought at their side!
Buck Roberts is leading a wagon train of railroad supplies and Jim Corkle and his henchman Loder are out to stop them by using white men dressed as Indians for the attacks.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/tKWL7HXWh38


Original title: Dawn on the Great Divide (1942)

Director: Howard Bretherton
Writers: Adele Buffington, James Oliver Curwood
Genres: Classics, Adventure, Drama, Romance, Western
Main cast: Buck Jones, Mona Barrie, Raymond Hatton, Robert Lowery, Rex Bell, Maude Eburne, Christine McIntyre, Betty Blythe
